game.name: Joy cooking Fresh Sandwich
game.description:
Trying out a new recipe is always a task filled with full of excitement and fun. Joy Cooking Fresh Sandwich is a free online cooking game where you will get a chance to accept a new challenge by helping Joy prepare a delicious sandwich shortly. Assist the girl to deliver all the orders of her customers timely and make her feel happy. Use all the fresh and tasty ingredients to make some mouth-watering sandwiches for the superheroes who are coming in starving.   

Joy has just started to sell extremely delicious sandwiches through a sandwich stand that maintains its location on the most crowded street in her town. The good news is the stand continues selling a great number of sandwiches and earning a handsome amount on a daily basis, so she asks for your assistance to make some lip-smacking sandwiches. Make sure that all her customers leave the stand with a smile. Do your best since all Joy customers are your favourite Disney Princesses and Superheroes. 

She relies on your chef skills, so please do not let her feel down in this brand new cooking game for girls and boys. Give a proper look to her sandwich stand from different types of stands, logos and roofs. Once it is done, decide who will be your very first customer of the day. Hope you will have fun and enjoy a lot while serving the best dish to her customers in this cool kitchen game for kids.
